<i>noun</i>: 의절 [의ː절] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>의절 [의ː절]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cutting off relationship; break of relations</dd><br>
<dd>맺었던 관계를 끊음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of severing relations with someone.</dd><br>
<dd>2. breach of friendship; disowning</dd><br>
<dd>친구나 친척 사이의 관계를 끊음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of severing relations with a friend or relative.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>